#==============================================================================#
  Tk::HideCursor
#==============================================================================#

Adds two methods to all Toplevel widgets that control whether the window stays
in the foreground.

Note for Win32 users:
This implementation requires teh Win32::API module.

Note for X-Windows users:
This implementation is very sucky - prepare to be dissapointed.

#==============================================================================#

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

If you are using Activestate perl, you can also install as a PPM:

   ppm install --location=http://brock-family.org/gavin/perl/ppm Tk::StayOnTop

#==============================================================================#

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires at least perl 5.6.0 and these other modules and libraries:

  Tk
  Win32::API (for windows users only)

